-- B y
-- 2012-02-21T20:41:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/how-ceos-spend-their-workday-study.html
Bloomberg's Duarte Geraldino 
reports on a study by  Harvard Business School  and London School 
of Economics researchers on how chief executive officers spend 
their time during their workday and how that affects the
performance of their companies.  He reports on Bloomberg Television's "InBusiness With 
Margaret Brennan." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:48
 